jnxRpf.name: jnxRpf
jnxRpf.contactinfo: Juniper Technical Assistance Center Juniper Networks, Inc. 1194 N. Mathilda Avenue Sunnyvale, CA 94089 E-mail: support@juniper.net
jnxRpf.description: This is Juniper Networks' enterprise-specific MIB for Reverse Path Forwarding (RPF)

jnxRpfStatsTable.name: jnxRpfStatsTable
jnxRpfStatsTable.description: This table contains statistics for traffic that is rejected due to RPF processing.

jnxRpfStatsEntry.name: jnxRpfStatsEntry
jnxRpfStatsEntry.description: Each entry in this table counts RPF-rejected traffic that is received on a particular interface and belongs to a particular address family.

jnxRpfStatsIfIndex.name: jnxRpfStatsIfIndex
jnxRpfStatsIfIndex.description: The ingress interface for traffic that is counted in this RpfStats entry.

jnxRpfStatsAddrFamily.name: jnxRpfStatsAddrFamily
jnxRpfStatsAddrFamily.description: The address family of this entry's traffic.

jnxRpfStatsPackets.name: jnxRpfStatsPackets
jnxRpfStatsPackets.description: The number of packets received on this interface, belonging to this address family, that have been rejected due to RPF processing.

jnxRpfStatsBytes.name: jnxRpfStatsBytes
jnxRpfStatsBytes.description: The number of bytes received on this interface, belonging to this address family, that have been rejected due to RPF processing.
